WEBVTT

00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:02.536
for crimes of the system,

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:07.320
the corruption that requires a fall guy,

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:10.136
a scapegoat,

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:13.016
so that the person who is responsible

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:14.240
could go free,

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:22.256
a broken system that routinely
vilifies the vulnerable,

00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:24.576
the poorest amongst us,

00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:27.696
people who cannot afford to pay bail

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:28.920
or bribes.